# Dependencies
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# Runtime data
data/downloads/
*.log
*.tmp
# SECURITY (2.0.18, L15): explicit ignore for the cli-debug.log
# file.  Although `*.log` already covers it, the explicit entry
# documents the file's purpose and protects against future
# `.gitignore` refactors that might (incorrectly) drop the
# generic `*.log` rule.  The default `debugLog()` location has
# moved to `~/.openclaw/extensions/xmpp/logs/cli-debug.log`
# (see src/shared/index.ts) so this file should not normally be
# created in the source tree, but we keep the ignore for
# belt-and-braces.
cli-debug.log
src/cli-debug.log

